CustomField.description: This formula field is used to provide ranking in number for a stakeholder.
CustomField.formula: IF( Support_Quotient__c <= 0, '0 out of 5', IF(Support_Quotient__c <= 4,'1 out of 5', IF(Support_Quotient__c <=10, '2 out of 5', IF(Support_Quotient__c <=16, '3 out of 5', IF(Support_Quotient__c <=22, '4 out of 5', '5 out of 5') ) ) ) )
CustomField.label: Ranking in Number
